![Screenshot](/assets/images/peptide_tools_screenshot.png)

A web application for peptide scientists. Allows users to calculate the analytical properties of the peptides and generated publication-quality data on the necessary synthetic protocols. Users can save and easily retrieve information on the different peptides and peptide building blocks.

---

Inside:

- Node.js
- MongoDB
- Pug
- JQuery

---

